\begin_layout Subsubsection*
6.2 Data Collection and Minimization
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Department Heads shall ensure that only data necessary for defined County business functions is collected.
 Department Heads shall not authorize collection of CJI,
 PII,
 or PHI beyond the data elements required to execute the specific legal authority under which the data is collected (statute,
 regulation,
 ordinance,
 court order,
 agreement,
 grant condition,
 or documented County business function authorized by law).
\end_layout

